description: 3456x2304 | 1273KB | JPG FILE | 1 sec. f/32 41mm | 800 ISO - COLOR  Fields of Immanence is a serie of Long-exposure photographs of digitally controlled Lasers. it’s the results of a research done bewteen 2013 and 2015 on Lasers modulated by lissajous and autonomous systems. Name is inspired by "planes of immanece" concept by Deleuze and Guattari,  The project was premiered in 2015 as audio-laser live set
